item.description:
Genre: Electronic, Stage & Screen
Style: Electro, Downtempo, Ambient
Year: 2023 (Released: March 10, 2023)
Source: Blu-ray (Super Deluxe Edition)

"Illuminate" is the thirteenth studio album of the music project Schiller created by the German electronic musician Christopher Von Deylen. With 8 number 1 albums and numerous gold & platinum awards, Schiller is Germany’s number 1 electronic artist. On his album Illuminate, von Deylen consistently continues his musical path, which recently led him back in the direction of edgy electronic beats with catchy melodies.
